Is there a way to use a field to populate the timezone?

this is causing errors for me:

{% if module.show_timestamp %}
	at {{ content.updated|format_date('K:mm a, z', '{{ module.timezone }}') }}
{% endif %}

It should be like this:
```{% if module.show_timestamp %}
	at {{ content.updated|format_date('K:mm a, z', module.timezone ) }}
{% endif %}```
